      <title>全球人工智能繁荣后，台积电一年来首次实现利润增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/tsmc-posts-first-profit-growth-in-a-year-after-global-ai-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[强劲的人工智能需求带动了全球最大代工芯片制造商台积电的增长，台积电公布了一年来的首次利润增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/tsmc-posts-first-profit-growth-in-a-year-after-global-ai-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 05:34:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华为推出新手机阵容加大对苹果的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/huawei-unveils-new-phone-lineup-to-ramp-up-the-pressure-on-apple</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华为技术有限公司周四发布了最新系列智能手机，在突破性的 Mate 60 设备帮助削弱了苹果公司在中国高端市场的主导地位后，维持了其发展势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/huawei-unveils-new-phone-lineup-to-ramp-up-the-pressure-on-apple</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 04:41:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>币安将其 10 亿美元“SAFU”应急基金转换为 USDC</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/binance-converts-billion-dollar-safu-emergency-fund-into-usdc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的加密货币交易所币安已将用户应急基金中持有的全部资产转换为美国公司 Circle Internet Financial 发行的稳定币 USDC。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/binance-converts-billion-dollar-safu-emergency-fund-into-usdc</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 04:20:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果首席执行官将与新加坡领导人会面，结束旋风亚洲之旅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/apple-ceo-tim-cook-meets-singapore-s-next-pm-lawrence-wong-as-he-wraps-asia-tour</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司首席执行官蒂姆·库克将在他多年来最广泛的东南亚之行结束时会见新加坡领导人，寻找新的增长市场和制造地点以抵消中国的不利因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/apple-ceo-tim-cook-meets-singapore-s-next-pm-lawrence-wong-as-he-wraps-asia-tour</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 02:46:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Google Play 反垄断协议被各国称为“合理”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/google-play-antitrust-accord-called-fair-reasonable-by-states</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州总检察长反驳了美国法官的疑虑，并敦促他批准一项和解方案，Alphabet Inc. 将支付 7 亿美元，以解决有关 Google Play 应用商店滥用市场支配力的反垄断指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/google-play-antitrust-accord-called-fair-reasonable-by-states</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:45:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美光科技将于下周宣布获得超过 60 亿美元的芯片资助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/micron-mu-to-get-over-6-billion-in-chips-act-grants-in-announcement-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的计算机内存芯片制造商美光科技公司 (Micron Technology Inc.) 准备从商务部获得 61 亿美元的拨款，以帮助支付国内工厂项目的费用，这是将半导体生产带回美国本土的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/micron-mu-to-get-over-6-billion-in-chips-act-grants-in-announcement-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 23:16:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃尔玛支持的 Ibotta 及其持有人在 IPO 中筹集了 5.77 亿美元，定价高于区间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/ibotta-holders-raise-577-million-in-ipo-priced-above-range</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ibotta Inc. 是一家数字营销软件公司，沃尔玛公司为支持者，一群股东在首次公开募股中筹集了约 5.773 亿美元，发行价高于市场区间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/ibotta-holders-raise-577-million-in-ipo-priced-above-range</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 22:58:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国因安全风险考虑对境外投资实施新限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/uk-mulls-new-curbs-on-outward-investment-over-security-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国正在考虑对人工智能和半导体等新兴技术的对外投资实施新的限制，理由是援助俄罗斯和中国等敌对国家存在潜在的安全风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/uk-mulls-new-curbs-on-outward-investment-over-security-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>教育科技公司 PowerSchool 因卖空报告而暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/education-tech-firm-powerschool-pwsc-slumps-on-spruce-point-short-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Spruce Point Capital Management LLC 表示，由于看到 PowerSchool Holdings Inc. 股票大幅下跌，因此该公司做空，该公司股价创下八个月来最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/education-tech-firm-powerschool-pwsc-slumps-on-spruce-point-short-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:54:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软认为俄罗斯业务放缓，中国影响投票的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/microsoft-sees-slowdown-in-russia-china-efforts-to-sway-us-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司的最新研究显示，俄罗斯正在努力在 2024 年大选前削弱美国对乌克兰的支持，而中国的影响力活动旨在分裂美国人并削弱他们对民主的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/microsoft-sees-slowdown-in-russia-china-efforts-to-sway-us-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:51:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
